# Project Workflow

## 1. Data Loading

* Imported dataset into Python using Pandas.
* Checked dataset structure and column information.
* Verified missing values and data types.

## 2. Data Cleaning

* Removed duplicate records.
* Handled missing/null values.
* Fixed inconsistent formatting.
* Converted columns into proper data types.
* Standardized categorical values.

## 3. Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)

* Performed statistical analysis.
* Identified trends and patterns.
* Created charts and visualizations.
* Compared different categories and metrics.

### EDA Visuals Included

* Bar Charts
* Pie Charts
* Histograms
* Line Charts
* Correlation Heatmaps

---

# SQL Analysis

## Database Operations

* Imported cleaned dataset into SQL database.
* Created tables and relationships.
* Wrote analytical SQL queries.

